---
---
<div class="space-y-3">
  <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/60 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur dark:border-white/[0.06] dark:bg-white/[0.02]" open>
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-800 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-100">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M22 16.92V19a2 2 0 01-2.18 2A19.72 19.72 0 013 5.18 2 2 0 015 3h2a2 2 0 012 1.72c.13 1.23.37 2.44.7 3.62a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11l-1.27 1.27a16 16 0 007.07 7.07l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c1.18.33 2.39.57 3.62.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg></span>
        <span x-show="lang==='es'">Tel\u00e9fono y llamadas</span>
        <span x-show="lang==='en'">Phone & calls</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="h-4 w-4 transition group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="border-t border-neutral-100 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-white/5 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <p x-show="lang==='es'"><b>CALL_PHONE</b>, <b>ANSWER_PHONE_CALLS</b> &mdash; realizar y contestar llamadas. <b>READ/WRITE_CALL_LOG</b> &mdash; gestionar historial cuando es app predeterminada.</p>
      <p x-show="lang==='en'"><b>CALL_PHONE</b>, <b>ANSWER_PHONE_CALLS</b> &mdash; place and answer calls. <b>READ/WRITE_CALL_LOG</b> &mdash; manage history as default app.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
  <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/60 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur dark:border-white/[0.06] dark:bg-white/[0.02]">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-800 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-100">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M9 20H4v-2a4 4 0 013-3.87"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><circle cx="15" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></span>
        <span x-show="lang==='es'">Contactos y agenda</span>
        <span x-show="lang==='en'">Contacts & address book</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="h-4 w-4 transition group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="border-t border-neutral-100 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-white/5 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <p x-show="lang==='es'"><b>READ/WRITE_CONTACTS</b> &mdash; mostrar, crear y editar contactos. Esc\u00e1ner QR y sincronizaci\u00f3n multi-cuenta.</p>
      <p x-show="lang==='en'"><b>READ/WRITE_CONTACTS</b> &mdash; display, create, and edit contacts. QR scanner and multi-account sync.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
  <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/60 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur dark:border-white/[0.06] dark:bg-white/[0.02]">
    <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-800 transition hover:text-accent dark:text-neutral-100">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent/10 text-accent"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"/></svg></span>
        <span x-show="lang==='es'">Extras opcionales</span>
        <span x-show="lang==='en'">Optional extras</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="h-4 w-4 transition group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </summary>
    <div class="border-t border-neutral-100 px-5 py-4 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:border-white/5 dark:text-neutral-400">
      <p x-show="lang==='es'"><b>Micr\u00f3fono</b> si usas grabaci\u00f3n o notas de voz. <b>C\u00e1mara</b> solo para fotos y QR. Todo opcional y revocable.</p>
      <p x-show="lang==='en'"><b>Microphone</b> if using recording or voice notes. <b>Camera</b> only for photos and QR. All optional and revocable.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>
